info.text: How do I find the claim code?
A gift card claim code is 14 or 15 characters long and will usually contain both letters and numbers (for example AS25-NJZ1JX-CZCP5).
If you have a plastic gift card, you may need to gently scratch or peel off the protective coating on the back of the card to reveal the claim code.
